&lt;li&gt;Work directly on high-priority initiatives across our SaaS products&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support discovery, documentation, and delivery for key product work streams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Join (and contribute to!) team rituals like sprint planning, retros, and roadmap reviews&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help scope and ship features from research through release&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Keep the team organized with clear requirements, thoughtful tracking, and great communication&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bring fresh eyes, user empathy, and curiosity to everything you touch&lt;/li&gt;
